871
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,370
looks so familiar to me.

872
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:34,250
Now it all makes sense.

873
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,690
He really is a familiar.

874
00:38:37,410 --> 00:38:38,160
Boys at his age

875
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:39,440
are so naughty.

876
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:40,690
Even dogs can't stand them.

877
00:38:40,690 --> 00:38:42,410
Boys are all naughty.

878
00:38:42,930 --> 00:38:43,690
When Tufang was little,

879
00:38:43,690 --> 00:38:44,960
he caused trouble in the Banner Battalion

880
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,560
every single day.

881
00:38:48,850 --> 00:38:50,160
Have you seen him

882
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:51,890
since you came back to China?

883
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:54,730
You mean your son?

884
00:38:56,250 --> 00:38:57,650
I remember back in Tokyo,

885
00:38:57,810 --> 00:38:58,850
you two

886
00:38:59,600 --> 00:39:01,040
didn't quite get along.

887
00:39:05,910 --> 00:39:08,110
I see his name in the papers all the time.

888
00:39:08,890 --> 00:39:09,890
Back then, who would've thought

889
00:39:09,890 --> 00:39:12,290
he'd become such a high-ranking official?

890
00:39:19,930 --> 00:39:20,640
When did you

891
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:21,850
come back from Japan?

892
00:39:23,730 --> 00:39:25,390
Two years later than your son.

893
00:39:26,730 --> 00:39:29,890
This kid was born in Tokyo?

894
00:39:30,730 --> 00:39:31,370
Yes.

895
00:39:33,730 --> 00:39:34,640
How old is he?

896
00:39:35,890 --> 00:39:36,690
By the end of the year,

897
00:39:36,690 --> 00:39:37,440
he'll turn five.

898
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,900
Six by traditional count.

899
00:39:41,330 --> 00:39:42,410
I'm getting old…

900
00:39:42,890 --> 00:39:44,350
not much left to ask about.

901
00:39:44,890 --> 00:39:46,780
My son's always off somewhere,

902
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:49,560
and his wife hasn't given him a child.

903
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:51,480
People say

904
00:39:52,250 --> 00:39:53,290
my family

905
00:39:53,310 --> 00:39:54,750
is on the rise right now,

906
00:39:55,210 --> 00:39:56,080
but actually,

907
00:39:56,600 --> 00:39:57,930
we still have

908
00:39:58,250 --> 00:39:59,210
our own worries.

909
00:40:00,410 --> 00:40:01,480
Where is your son?

910
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:03,040
He's in Baoding,

911
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:06,840
accompanying the Prince Regent's
younger brother on a trip.

912
00:40:06,930 --> 00:40:09,130
This wasn't even supposed to be his job.

913
00:40:13,350 --> 00:40:14,410
Where are we going?

914
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:15,410
Second Lord,

915
00:40:15,410 --> 00:40:16,270
we're almost there.

916
00:40:16,270 --> 00:40:17,320
Almost?

917
00:40:17,410 --> 00:40:18,960
We've been running around all day.

918
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:21,120
We don't have
the energy to wander with you.

919
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:23,440
Exactly. Where are we going?

920
00:40:24,970 --> 00:40:26,260
Second Lord, please.

921
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,880
Welcome.

922
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,510
So considerate.

923
00:40:32,680 --> 00:40:33,850
Sirs, come on in.

924
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:37,640
Hurry, hurry.

925
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:03,410
Make sure they're entertained.

926
00:41:03,410 --> 00:41:05,850
Don't let them out

927
00:41:05,850 --> 00:41:08,250
until noon tomorrow.

928
00:41:08,410 --> 00:41:10,890
They must stay until tomorrow noon.

929
00:41:11,640 --> 00:41:12,440
Understand?

930
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:13,640
Yes.

931
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,810
Don't worry.

932
00:41:15,810 --> 00:41:16,600
Officer Li,

933
00:41:16,890 --> 00:41:19,120
leave it to me.

934
00:41:26,410 --> 00:41:27,960
So sinful.

935
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,600
There goes a whole week's worth

936
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:31,960
of grocery money.

937
00:41:39,810 --> 00:41:41,640
Sirs, have a good night.

938
00:41:41,850 --> 00:41:43,890
I still have military duties to attend to.

939
00:41:43,890 --> 00:41:45,090
I must excuse myself.

940
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:48,600
Take good care of these two lords.

941
00:41:48,850 --> 00:41:49,810
Make sure they're not slighted.

942
00:41:49,810 --> 00:41:50,640
Understood.

943
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:53,410
I shall take my leave first.

944
00:42:01,160 --> 00:42:02,330
Well,

945
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,600
why were the Second Lord and his men

946
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:05,930
so well-behaved today?

947
00:42:08,890 --> 00:42:10,210
How did the audit go?

948
00:42:10,890 --> 00:42:11,890
Chairman,

949
00:42:11,890 --> 00:42:12,960
the audit is complete.

950
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,480
The lords were very pleased.

951
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,680
They're resting in the guest rooms now.

952
00:42:17,890 --> 00:42:18,890
Good.

953
00:42:20,890 --> 00:42:21,640
Tufang.

954
00:42:22,640 --> 00:42:23,560
I'm exhausted.

955
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,890
You two chat out here.

956
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:28,890
I'm turning in for the night.
